merce thing=E2=80=A6 doesn=E2=80=99t really work! You can have content, and=
 you can have commerce, but you can=E2=80=99t put a checkout page on an art=
icle and expect the reader to become the consumer. (Now, when the content i=
s commerce, like a newsletter about shopping, that=E2=80=99s different. Rec=
ommendations work when there=E2=80=99s a linkout.)

